---
const helps = [
  'A clear reproduction (proof-of-concept welcome)',
  'The repo + commit SHA, if relevant',
  'Your assessment of severity and impact',
  'Whether you intend to disclose publicly, and when',
];
---

<section id="disclosure" class="security-section paper" data-security-section>
  <div class="security-container audit-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="bb-eyebrow">Responsible disclosure</div>
      <h2 class="bb-display-l">Found something?<br />Tell us first.</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        If you’ve found a vulnerability in our clients, our protocol, or our
        infrastructure, we want to hear about it before anyone else does.
      </p>
      <p>
        We’ll acknowledge within <strong>48 hours</strong>
        and aim to resolve high-severity issues within
        <strong>14 days</strong>. We will credit you
        publicly with your permission, on this page, when the fix ships.
      </p>
      <p class="fine">
        We do not yet run a paid bug bounty. We are a small team and would rather
        spend that money on shipping fixes than on programs we can’t honour.
        If we change that, this paragraph will change with it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="report-card">
      <div class="t-label">How to report</div>
      <div class="report-block">
        <div>Email</div>
        <a href="mailto:security@beebeeb.io">security@beebeeb.io</a>
      </div>
      <div class="report-block">
        <div>PGP</div>
        <p>We do not yet publish a PGP key. Coming soon.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="report-label">What helps us</div>
        <ul>
          {helps.map((item) => (
            <li><span>→</span><span>{item}</span></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .audit-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .audit-grid .bb-eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .audit-grid h2 {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }

  .audit-grid p {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .audit-grid .lead {
    font-size: 15.5px;
  }

  .audit-grid strong {
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .audit-grid .fine {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .report-card {
    padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: oklch(0.92 0.005 80);
  }

  .report-card .t-label {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    color: var(--amber);
  }

  .report-block {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .report-block div,
  .report-label {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    color: oklch(0.6 0.01 70);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .report-label {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .report-block a {
    color: var(--amber);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .report-block p {
    margin: 0;
    color: oklch(0.78 0.01 80);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .report-card ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    color: oklch(0.78 0.01 80);
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .report-card li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .report-card li span:first-child {
    color: var(--amber);
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .audit-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 36px;
    }
  }
</style>
